---
title: Steak and Asparagus Platter with Roasted Sweet Potatoes and Garlic Bread
description: This shareable platter turns regular steak and potatoes into a party! Do you have picky eaters at your table? Leave the tarragon out of the creamy herb sauce, then just sprinkle over the plates for anyone who loves it!
